Chief Product/Development Ofcr of Nutanix (NASDAQ:NTNX), Potti Sunil, sells 10,000 shares worth $225,739
According to Nutanix's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jul 19 05:10 PM, company Chief Product/Development Ofcr, Potti Sunil disclosed selling 10,000 shares at a cost of $22.57. At the time of this transaction (Jul 17), this trade was worth $225,739 in total. As of Jul 17, Potti Sunil now owns 131,382 shares in total worth about $3,207,034.62. 
For the last few recent trades made by Nutanix (NASDAQ:NTNX) Chief Product/Development Ofcr, Potti Sunil, we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Jun 26: Sold 30,000 shares at the rate of $20.00 per share. Total worth of this trade was $600,000. Total number of shares owned as of Jun 26 were 114,165
SEC Form 4 filing: Jun 15: Sold 55,000 shares at the rate of $17.33 per share. Total worth of this trade was $953,194. Total number of shares owned as of Jun 15 were 144,165




