Nutanix Appoints Sunil Potti as Senior Vice President of Engineering and Product Management | Business Wire


























































Nutanix Appoints Sunil Potti as Senior Vice President of Engineering 
      and Product Management






      Former Citrix VP and GM Brings Broad Portfolio of Product, Engineering 
      and General Management Experience
    









