Background

		Mr. Sunil Potti has been the Chief Product & Development Officer at Nutanix, Inc since February 18, 2016 and served as its Senior Vice President of Engineering and Product Management from January 2015 to February 18, 2016. With more than 20 years of datacenter and networking experience, Mr. Potti joined Nutanix from Citrix , where he led the Citrix NetScaler business for over five years of record growth. Throughout his career, he has built industry-leading products and ... scaled teams against intense competition from large incumbent players. At Nutanix he oversee all product functions including product strategy, development, and quality. He joined Citrix from F5 Networks, where he was vice president of the acceleration and virtualization group. Prior to F5, he co-founded and led all product efforts for application-oriented networking at Cisco. Previous to this, he was an early employee at Synchrony, a CRM startup acquired by Divine, where he headed products and engineering. Mr. Potti holds a masters degree in computer science from Pennsylvania State University.Read Full Background




