Cisco Blog  >  Author Biographies

 

Sunil Potti


Senior Vice President and General Manager
							NetScaler Product Group, Citrix
															Guest Blogger
													








						Sunil Potti is vice president and general manager of the NetScaler Product Group at Citrix.  In this role, Sunil leads the P&L for the Citrix NetScaler product line, the cloud networking platform powering many of the world’s largest clouds. Prior to this role, Sunil was the vice president of product marketing and product management for the Cloud Networking group at Citrix. He joined Citrix from F5 Networks, where he was the vice president of the Acceleration and Virtualization group. Sunil spent many years prior at Cisco and Sybase. He holds a master’s degree in computer science and engineering from Pennsylvania State University.					


